# 詞: 銀包

1. 佢好愛收銀包，每次去銀行都帶好多錢。 (He loves to keep silver bags; he always carries a lot of money when he goes to the bank.)
2. 佢話銀包夠多，可以買好多新衣服。 (He says the silver bag has enough money to buy many new clothes.)
3. 我唔知銀包夠唔夠，但我想先買個新手機。 (I don't know if the silver bag is enough; but I want to buy a new mobile phone first.)
4. 佢家銀包好厚，可以養好多隻貓。 (His family's silver bag is very thick; it can support many cats.)
5. 佢話銀包夠，但其實佢只係想買個新包包。 (He says the silver bag is enough, but actually he just wants to buy a new handbag.)
6. 我唔懂銀包係咪夠，但我想先買個新包包。 (I don't know if the silver bag is enough; but I want to buy a new handbag first.)
7. 佢話銀包夠多，可以帶去好多地方玩。 (He says the silver bag has enough money to take to many places to play.)
8. 我唔知銀包夠唔夠，但我想先買個新包包。 (I don't know if the silver bag is enough; but I want to buy a new handbag first.)
9. 佢家銀包好厚，可以養好多隻貓。 (His family's silver bag is very thick; it can support many cats.)
10. 佢話銀包夠，可以買好多新衣服。 (He says the silver bag has enough money to buy many new clothes.) [end of text]


